This series was shown across Latin American countries in the early 80s, with the title "San Kuo Kai". From the total of 27 episodes, only 25 were ever dubbed and shown in Latin America. I used to watch this as a kid, and really liked it.

Torrent contains the 25 espisodes aired in Latin America.

Audio is in Spanish.
